'''阿马加巨龙'''（[[属名|属名]]：''Amargatitanis''，意为“{{le|阿马加组|La Amarga Formation|阿马加}}的巨人”）是[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[内乌肯省|内乌肯省]][[早白垩世|早白垩世]]（[[巴列姆阶|巴列姆阶]]）{{le|阿马加组|La Amarga Formation}}的一[[属|属]][[叉龙科|叉龙科]][[蜥脚类|蜥脚类]][[恐龙|恐龙]]。

== 分类 ==
[[正模标本|正模标本]]'''MACN PV N53'''由[[约瑟·波拿巴|约瑟·波拿巴]]（José Fernando Bonaparte）于1983年3月收集，由两节尾椎、一个右[[坐骨|坐骨]]及部分右后肢组成。尽管在原描述中归入[[泰坦巨龙类|泰坦巨龙类]]，但后期研究者对此提出质疑，指出被视为该属{{le|合模标本|Syntype}}的[[肩胛骨|肩胛骨]]（MACN PV N34）及六节尾椎（MACN PV N51）的发现地与MACN PV N53不同，因此其假定的泰坦巨龙类特征无效。<ref name=SA07>{{cite journal |last=Apesteguía |first=Sebastián |year=2007 |title=The sauropod diversity of the La Amarga Formation (Barremian), Neuquén (Argentina) |journal=Gondwana Research |volume=12 |issue=4 |pages=533–546 |doi=10.1016/j.gr.2007.04.007|bibcode=2007GondR..12..533A }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = D'Emic | first1 = M. D. | year = 2012 | title = The early evolution of titanosauriform sauropod dinosaurs | url =https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/bitstream/2027.42/94293/1/j.1096-3642.2012.00853.x.pdf | journal = Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society | volume = 166 | issue = 3| pages = 624–671 | doi = 10.1111/j.1096-3642.2012.00853.x | doi-access = free }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1111/zoj.12029|title=Osteology of the Late Jurassic Portuguese sauropod dinosaur ''Lusotitan atalaiensis'' (Macronaria) and the evolutionary history of basal titanosauriforms|journal=Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society|volume=168|pages=98–206|year=2013|last1=Mannion|first1=Philip D.|last2=Upchurch|first2=Paul|last3=Barnes|first3=Rosie N.|last4=Mateus|first4=Octávio|url=http://docentes.fct.unl.pt/sites/default/files/omateus/files/mannion_et_al_2013_sauropod_lusotitan_portugal.pdf}}</ref>巴勃罗·埃雷·加林纳（Pablo Ariel Gallina）2016年的研究将其重新归入[[叉龙科|叉龙科]]。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Gallina | first1 = Pablo Ariel | year = 2016 | title = Reappraisal Of The Early Cretaceous Sauropod Dinosaur ''Amargatitanis macni'' (Apesteguía, 2007), From Northwestern Patagonia, Argentina |journal= Cretaceous Research | volume =  64| pages =  79–87 |doi= 10.1016/j.cretres.2016.04.002 |url= https://www.researchgate.net/publication/300420946 }}</ref>

